&bull;社會及政治組織從業員工會<br />\n&bull;香港旅遊業革新總工會籌委會"},{"pid":"fd4a65743e9e5bd21dbe7ae990d7b588bfd8b208","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"9/30"},{"pid":"f630c282e4938cdf4dabb818d5da7cf531bb0619","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:51:29.000Z","msg":"10/30"},{"pid":"2ff971388bda35ba55059397b9bc52ecbd43b8f2","tid":1839191,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"工會防疫聯合記者會<br />\n【武漢肺炎襲港 全城自救抗疫】<br />\n<br />\n近日武漢肺炎疫情日趨嚴重，本港已有多宗高度懷疑個案，其中更有二人證實確診武漢肺炎。港人毋忘沙士的陰霾，促請香港政府回應，但港府仍後知後覺，未就疫情計劃全面應變措施，防止病毒蔓延。多個來自不同界別工會將於2020年1月24日舉行新聞發佈會，就近日武漢肺炎作回應。"},{"pid":"4ce44ad680a61827f8ff58c778096ff44ba979d4","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"11/30"},{"pid":"d63c4166a0acd6f355d4c3f94bb529ac4f169f4d","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"12/30"},{"pid":"f70820ddafacdbb231073292d487c2ebcce75b84","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"13/30"},{"pid":"8274050a5e1b85a1f8fae31a89a6c08bb8b52f52","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"14/30"},{"pid":"bc98a4679888fcd8b04474907c2cc2a1b8052b0c","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"15/30"},{"pid":"d1ad54ab0f8e83ad7838d3b8470e6191b6d93e08","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"16/30"},{"pid":"42a7ba7a9c952e355f3ca6c18e8e976b56e5eeec","tid":1839191,"uid":57994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"17/30"},{"pid":"e8929c9a4acfbb996155b2db68f25777a7b9e1be"